This paper deals with sentiment analysis, which is a subfield of natural language processing (NLP). Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also discusses the use of distant supervision, which is a common technique in information retrieval (IR) and machine learning (LG). Hence, cs.IR and cs.LG are also likely categories. The paper also involves the use of machine learning models, which falls under the category of artificial intelligence (AI). Therefore, cs.AI is another possible category. Finally, the paper deals with the analysis of electronic messages, which could be considered a subfield of cybersecurity (CY). Hence, cs.CY is also a possible category.
